 of the game, but also hit out at organisers after he was unable to keep his water cool, saying: 'It was tough conditions, there is no doubt about it.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 744}, {\"ngram\": \"his water\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"tough conditions\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"no doubt\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I need to play more in this sort of heat, and obviously, going toAmerica, I will get more used to that.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this sort\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was really hot out there today.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We were both trying our best to put out some good tennis.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some good tennis\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Part of it's physicality but I said to the referee, it's pretty poor that the players have to drink hot water when we are playing in those conditions.\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Part\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"physicality\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"the referee\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"hot water\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"those conditions\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's important we have good fridges to keep our water cool.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good fridges\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"our water\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's so tough to recover when you are just not replenishing properly.'\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of fridges, players have been given refillable bottles and water fountains, with organisers looking to be more environmentally friendly and make Paris 2024 the greenest games in history.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1491, \"end\": 1501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.541822198577927e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fridges\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1356}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"refillable bottles\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"water fountains\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is no escape from the heat, even at the change of ends.\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no escape\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"the heat\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"the change\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"ends\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have not played in much hotter conditions than that.\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"much hotter con